### =====================================================================
### Comment API  (base route: api/comment/)
### TagComment: 101 Released, 102 InQueue, 103 Rejected, 201 Private
### TagReaction: 101 Like, 102 Dislike
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Create - on a product
POST {{host}}/api/comment/Create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "description": "Great product!",
  "score": 4.5,
  "reaction": 101,
  "tags": [101],
  "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Create - reply (with parentId) on a blog
POST {{host}}/api/comment/Create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "description": "I agree with the above.",
  "score": 0,
  "tags": [101],
  "blogId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "parentId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Read - by product
POST {{host}}/api/comment/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Read - by user
POST {{host}}/api/comment/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### ReadById
POST {{host}}/api/comment/ReadById
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Update
POST {{host}}/api/comment/Update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "description": "Edited comment",
  "score": 5
}

